MetaLayer,is,a,data,visualization,service,that,allows,users,to,drag,and,drop,data,of,various,types,including,imagery,for,analysis,and,data,visualization,MetaLayer,can,be,used,by,a,variety,of,industries,including,research,and,journalism,The,MetaLayer,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,and,data,of,MetaLayer,with,other,applications,and,services,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,data,information,and,metadata,accessing,images,and,information,about,images,and,uploading,data,and,images